msgid ""
"For this release, we polished some pixels, waved a few bugs goodbye, and worke"
"d behind the scenes to make the WordPress experience smoother for our app user"
"s."
msgstr ""

#. translators: This is a standard chunk of text used to tell a user what's new with a release when nothing major has changed.
msgctxt "standard-whats-new-3"
