msgid ""
"It may look the same,\n"
"but we shined and buffed the code.\n"
"Small changes add up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "v26.7-whats-new"
msgid ""
"112% of our team loved the big changes we made to the Stats section. (Some peo"
"ple may have voted twice; we can’t say for sure.)\n"
"\n"
"- There’s a new Ads tab where you can see important WordAds data like the numb"
"er of ads served and revenue earned.\n"
"- We added a UTM tab so you can see source and medium for your site traffic. T"
"here’s also a Devices view that shows you which devices your visitors used.\n"
"- When you select “Today” or another daily period in the Post Stats screen, yo"
"u’ll see “Last 7 days” instead of hourly data that doesn’t exist. We can’t pre"
"dict the future just yet.\n"
"- We fixed some visual issues with charts and made design improvements through"
"out the Stats section.\n"
"\n"
"We solved a caching issue on the Insights screen that would display a blank Po"
"sting Activity area. Now you can always see what you’ve been up to.\n"
"\n"
"We made small visual improvements on the Activity Logs screen, like titles, ic"
"ons, and colors.\n"
"\n"
"We added Custom Post Types as an experimental feature. Test it out and let us "
"know what you think. #science\n"
"\n"
"One last thing: if your site is authenticated with an application password, yo"
"u don’t need to have XML-RPC enabled. The downside is that only limited featur"
"es are available. Once enabled, you can get those features back.\n"
msgstr ""

